snippet.title: Project Nightmares Case 36: Henrietta Kedward - Trailer 2
snippet.description:
Project Nightmares is an horror survival game, unique in its genre, with a procedural structure of objects and levels makes it a unique experience.
(The trailer was made recording the in game) 

IMPORTANT: This new update (version 1.0.008) will be available October 1st
Steam Early Access: https://store.steampowered.com/app/812070/
